335
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:05,856
I feel dizzy.

336
00:25:05,856 --> 00:25:06,944
Do you want to throw up?

337
00:25:07,839 --> 00:25:08,864
Just take some rest.

338
00:25:12,319 --> 00:25:14,279
