341
00:25:27,440 --> 00:25:28,480
Do you know her?

342
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:30,624
No.

343
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,359
What's your password?

344
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,780
I'll tell you,

345
00:25:45,780 --> 00:25:47,059
