00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:20,352
<i>♫ I can't delete them ♫</i>

386
00:28:21,284 --> 00:28:27,008
<i>♫ Time drips away bit by bit ♫</i>

387
00:28:27,008 --> 00:28:32,672
<i>♫ Memories are scattered everywhere ♫</i>

388
00:28:32,672 --> 00:28:39,744
<i>♫ The passing trees cast shadows like you ♫</i>

389
00:28:41,188 --> 00:28:44,352
<i>♫ Fading away ♫</i>

