402
00:29:56,804 --> 00:30:02,432
<i>♫ The surge of longing burns within ♫</i>

403
00:30:02,432 --> 00:30:08,800
<i>♫ Waiting to find the answer at the end ♫</i>

404
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:11,968
<i>♫ Accelerating against the wind ♫</i>

405
00:30:11,968 --> 00:30:14,880
<i>♫ Is your pride ♫</i>

406
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:18,048
<i>♫ And also ♫</i>

407
00:30:18,048 --> 00:30:23,104
<i>♫ My ultimate goal ♫</i>

