410
00:30:38,740 --> 00:30:39,872
What time is it now?

411
00:30:39,872 --> 00:30:41,400
Don't you know this would hold up my work?

412
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,240
I didn't forget.

413
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:46,240
I knocked,

414
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,559
