452
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:48,000
I think

453
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,679
Chen Mobai is really considerate.

454
00:33:50,679 --> 00:33:52,060
He said he doesn't know

455
00:33:52,060 --> 00:33:53,319
