470
00:35:08,079 --> 00:35:09,152
What happened?

471
00:35:10,599 --> 00:35:12,719
I thought you were on a forum.

472
00:35:13,239 --> 00:35:15,159
Zhao Yingning suddenly came to your room,

473
00:35:15,760 --> 00:35:17,400
