00:37:47,012 --> 00:37:51,012
<i>[In Operation]</i>

526
00:38:01,039 --> 00:38:02,112
<i>Brother,</i>

527
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:06,920
<i>what should I do now?</i>

528
00:38:31,039 --> 00:38:32,440
<i>I've already lost you.</i>

